[normal]1.1 RTPI Trustees consider that realistic CE salary to be important to attract
[normal] the best candidate to further the work of the Institute and Charity.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]1.2 RTPI Trustees are well aware of their Charity requirements regarding making best use of money.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]1.3 CE salary levels should remain within the control of Trustees.
